    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes a simplified method for extending the Link State PDU (LSP) space beyond the 256 LSP limit.  This method is intended as a preferred replacement for the method defined in RFC 3786. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
